703551f-b.title: Brooklyn: Church Avenue - Chester Avenue
703551f-b.text:
(1)
3221-3237 Church Ave., at the N.E. corner of Chester Ave. The
frame house is known as No. El, showing a rear view of the Martense-Story
Heuse.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, showing side of house, facing on Chester Ave.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(3)
The same, from another angle.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(4)
The same, as No. 2, from a different angle.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
